fs.fibu2.data.format
Interface JournalExport

All Known Implementing Classes:
CSVTableExport, OldJournalExport, StandardJournalExport, VeryOldJournalExport
public interface JournalExport

A JournalExport is a class which can export an fsfibu 2 Journal to a file in a certain format, e.g. csv.

Author:
Simon Hampe
